title: Lombardi’s Week 13 Reactions | GM Street (Ep. 358)
description:
The Eagles keep their playoff hopes alive, the Chargers survive in Pittsburgh, and the Packers show Mike McCarthy the door. Plus: this week’s awards.

Hosts: Michael Lombardi and Tate Frazier
